The initial Knowmine app: **AI-powered scanning**, an inventory with locations,
categories, and tags, session auth, and a Bun + SvelteKit + Drizzle/LibSQL
monorepo. The toolchain migrated to **tsgo**, dependencies were upgraded to
latest, and docs were rebranded from Proomptal to Aylith.
